data.description: Welcome home to 6694 Axtel Drive! There is so much potential in this 1 story end unit condo! Condo offers 2 large bedrooms, 2 full baths, 2 car attached garage, HUGE laundry and utility space that could double as office space, mudroom, pantry, or anything you can dream up! Outside you will find a fenced yard, 2 parking spaces for this unit and a large parking area next door for guests. Brand new HVAC system installed 1 week ago!
